content: It is called WA~ Stadium by picking the weakness of Welcome to Ansan. It is also the home stadium of K-League Ansan Greeners. There is no match where there is always a shout, so it is quiet today.. The autumn leaves and the quiet stadium are very charming.
This gymnasium in Anshan City is not bad, the facilities are very good, and relatively large.
There are really occasional national football games!
love han river! especially not to miss the ramen making by the river at the convenience stores, super memorable and it somehow just tastes better haha
